  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">5: MotionDesigner</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading2" style="page-break-before:always;"><image src="5r.gif" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" style="font-size:10pt; vertical-align:baseline;" figurelistinclude="0"></image><text styleclass="Normal">&#32;</text>MotionDesigner</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table">Use <text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="false">MotionDesigner</text> to add, name and design motions. Each motion has a unique name that is shown in the <text styleclass="Interface">Motion name-tab</text>. of <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">MotionDesigner</text>.</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table">When you design a motion, you can use a <text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text> to link it to a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Motion-Driven-Part" styleclass="Interface">Motion-Part</link> or <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-POP-Motion-Driven-Point" styleclass="Interface">Motion-Point</link> in <text styleclass="VariableName-IT">MechDesigner.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">To Link a Motion to a Motion-Part</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Table"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="2" style="border-width:1px; border-spacing:0px; cell-border-width:0px; border-color:#993300; border-style:solid;">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <list id="0" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;&#32;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="false" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">Add a </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo"> to the </text><text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="1" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text style="font-style:normal;">Click</text><text style="font-family:Arial; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">&#32;</text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-FB-Kinematics" styleclass="T_Menu">Kinematics FB toolbar</link><text styleclass="T_Menu"> &gt; Motion FB</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-style:normal;">Click</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text> is now in the <text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text>. </para>
          <list id="2" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;&#32;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="false" legalstyle="false" startfrom="2" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Open the <text styleclass="Element">Motion FB dialog-box</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td style="border-top:none; border-right:none; border-bottom:none;">
                <list id="3" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-style:normal;">Double-click </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">a </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> in the </text><text styleclass="Interface">graphic-area</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> or </text><text styleclass="Interface">Assembly-Tree</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="VariableName-IT">- or -</para>
                <list id="4" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="B Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="SeeAlso">See </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-How-to-Open-a-Dialog-Box" styleclass="SeeAlso">How to Open a Dialog-Box</link><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:bold;">&#32;</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Element">Motion FB dialog-box</text> is now <text styleclass="Interface">open</text>. </para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:232px;">
          <para styleclass="Normal"><image src="MD-Dialog-MotionFB.png" scale="-99.90%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td>
          <list id="5" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="3" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP">Edit the Motion FB dialog-box:</li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text styleclass="Separator-Header">Motion Parameters </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Select Motion</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="6" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets">Click the down-arrow in the list box,<text styleclass="Body Text"> to show the list of motions that are the </text><text styleclass="VariableName">Motion name-tabs</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered">Click the motion name that you want to link to the </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered">.</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Output Option</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="7" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Parameter">Reset output</text> :<text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"> Default option, and is used most frequently. </text></li>
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter">Accumulate output : </text> Select <text styleclass="VariableName">only</text> when the motion is a progressive motion (e.g. indexing)</li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Parameter-Header">Output Data Type</para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="8" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text styleclass="Parameter">Motion </text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted">: Default option, use in most cases</text></li>
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="Parameter">Linear or Rotary</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered"> : Select when you connect the </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered"> to a </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion-Path FB </text><text styleclass="Body Text">or </text><text styleclass="Element">Math FB.</text></li>
                </list>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text">Click <image src="OK-tiny-13-17.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption" figurelistinclude="0"></image> to close the <text styleclass="Element">Motion FB dialog-Box</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td colspan="2">
          <list id="9" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#83;&#84;&#69;&#80;&#32;&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#58;&#32;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="false" legalstyle="false" startfrom="4" styleclass="HowTo STEP" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
            <li styleclass="HowTo STEP"><text styleclass="VariableName">Connect wires to the input-connector and from the output-connector.</text></li>
          </list>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Block" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
            <tr style="vertical-align:top">
              <td>
                <list id="10" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Bullets" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="Bullets"><text style="font-style:normal;">Connect a wire to the input-connector of the </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text><text styleclass="VariableName">&#32;</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">Usually, (but not always), connect a wire from the output of a <text styleclass="Element">Linear-Motion FB</text> or a <text styleclass="Element">Gearing FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> to the input-connector of the </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text">.</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">When you cycle the model, the motion-values at its input-connector are the <text styleclass="Interface">X-axis</text>&#32;<text style="font-style:normal;">motion-values</text> of the <text styleclass="VariableName">Motion</text> you select in <text styleclass="VariableName">STEP 3</text>.</para>
                <list id="10" type="ol" listtype="decimal" formatstring="&#37;&#48;&#58;&#115;&#46;" format-charset="DEFAULT_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-family:&apos;Segoe UI Semibold&apos;; font-size:8pt; color:#000000;">
                  <li styleclass="HowTo Numbered"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" style="font-style:normal;">Connect a wire from the output-connector of the </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text></li>
                </list>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">Usually (not always), connect a wire from the <text styleclass="Element">Motion FB</text> to the input of a <text styleclass="Element">Motion-Dimension FB</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> or a </text><text styleclass="Element">Motion-Path FB</text></para>
                <para styleclass="Body Table">When you cycle the model, the motion-values at the output-connector are the <text styleclass="Interface">Y-axis</text> motion-values of the <text styleclass="VariableName">Motion</text> you select in Select Motion drop-down box (see <text styleclass="VariableName">STEP 3).</text></para>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
